definitions.definition: A species which reproduces by sexual rather than asexual reproduction, or a member of such a species.
A person who experiences sexual attraction , a person who has interest in or desire for sex ( especially as contrasted with an asexual ) .

main_definition: ( biology ) A species which reproduces by sexual rather than asexual reproduction, or a member of such a species.
